<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_10" id="4v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_10_r2l21"><expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> <expan>Mıchelſperg<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒüm <expan>bode<ex>n</ex>ſtein</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_10_r2l22"><expan>Pfleg<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒü Lengfeld . </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_10_r2l23"><expan>Lıeb<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> / Als Jr vns <expan>geſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt wie etlıche die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_10_r2l24">die yecʒund von deʒ Lantfrids <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> auf <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> veld <expan>geweſe<ex>n</ex></expan> ſind </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_10_r2l25">v̈ber ew geloffen ſein vnd <expan>wolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ew <expan>erſlage<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / etc . <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_10_r2l26">vvir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brıef vvol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> / vnd heten ew die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ıht <expan>vnʒeitlıch</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_10_line_1573559159857_210">getan <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> v̈bervaren / Das 
<add><ab facs="#facs_10_line_1578388102852_1061"><gap reason="damaged"/> wir niht </ab><ab facs="#facs_10_line_1578388107232_1066">vnd </ab></add> wer vns 
<del rend="strikethrough">ʒemal leide </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_10_line_1573559116022_185">nicht lıeb </ab></add> / . Nu hat vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_10_r2l31"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Hercʒog Johans von <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan> ſache <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> einen tag </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_10_r2l32">beſchieden / gen <expan>Amb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> auf den nehſten Montag / dar cʒü etlıch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_10_r2l33"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> Rats <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> ſüllen / vnd den vvöllen wir alſo <expan>empfelh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mit </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_10_r2l34"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> des Hercʒogen gnaden / vnd auch mit ew <expan>ſelb<ex>er</ex></expan> davon </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_10_r2l35">cʒereden / vnd vvo wir ew lıeb vnd dinſt <expan>beweıſe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>möht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_10_r2l36">teten vvir allcʒeit <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ıııj̃ <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Egidij </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_10" id="4v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>
<expan>Michelsperg<ex>er</ex></expan> czüm
                            <expan>Bode<ex>n</ex>stein</expan>, <expan>pfleg<ex>er</ex></expan> czü
                        Lengfeld</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt, wie etliche die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, die yeczund von dez lantfrids
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> auf <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> veld
                                <expan>gewese<ex>n</ex></expan> sind, über ew geloffen sein und
                                <expan>wolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ew <expan>erslage<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc. <expan>Hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brief wol
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> und heten ew die
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> iht <expan>unzeitlich</expan> getan
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> übervaren das <add><app>
<note><gap reason="damaged"/></note>
</app> wir niht und</add> wer uns <add>nicht lieb</add>. Nu hat uns
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> herczog Johans von
                            <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan> sache <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> einen
    tag beschieden gen <expan>Amb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> auf den <app><note><q type="date">nehsten montag</q>02.09.1409</note></app>,
                        dar czü etlich <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> rats
                            <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> süllen. Und den wöllen wir also
                                <expan>empfelh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mit <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, des herczogen, gnaden und auch mit ew
                                <expan>selb<ex>er</ex></expan> davon czereden; und wo wir ew lieb
                        und dinst <expan>beweise<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>möht<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, das teten wir allczeit
                            <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iiii <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Egidii.</ab></div>
</div></body>
